title: Momiji Japanese Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fast-casual sushi restaurant on Hwy 101 across from The Mill Casino. Sushi selections include asparagus tempura roll, avocado roll, cucumber roll, mango roll, vegetable roll, and inari. Also offered are cucumber salad, wakame seaweed salad, edamame, agedashi tofu, yam tempura, and miso soup with choice of udon, soba, or rice noodles. Note the fryer is likely shared with non-veg.
